13:07.360 --> 13:09.720
I was a police officer in Arvada,
Colorado for a couple years.

13:09.800 --> 13:13.640
Then I was a police officer
in Charlotte for about ten years.

13:13.960 --> 13:18.080
When did you first get involved
in the case of State vs. Michael Peterson?

13:18.520 --> 13:20.960
About a week after December the 9th.

13:21.600 --> 13:23.400
Of what year?

13:24.200 --> 13:27.280
- Ten years ago. 2001.
- 2001? Alright.

13:27.360 --> 13:30.960
In connection with this hearing,
did you review

13:31.040 --> 13:35.520
all of the discovery that was provided
by the state of North Carolina

13:35.600 --> 13:38.480
in response to the orders
that were issued by Judge Hudson?

13:38.560 --> 13:41.080
I did. Well over 100,000 pages,

13:41.160 --> 13:43.480
many CDs, and disks, and...

13:43.800 --> 13:47.000
- And you reviewed all of that? Alright.
- Unfortunately.

13:47.080 --> 13:51.360
Did you review some reports
that Duane Deaver

13:51.760 --> 13:53.920
either authored or was mentioned in?

13:54.040 --> 13:55.080
Yes, sir.

13:59.080 --> 14:00.320
How many cases

14:00.400 --> 14:05.000
of bloodstain pattern analysis
or evaluations have you actually worked?

14:05.840 --> 14:09.120
I don’t know for sure, but it would be
somewhere around 200

14:09.200 --> 14:11.480
that I have written reports on myself.

14:11.560 --> 14:14.640
Now, that doesn’t include the number
of cases that I have

14:14.720 --> 14:16.520
looked at as part of my training.

14:16.840 --> 14:19.760
And I continue to provide help
to others who are in training.

14:19.840 --> 14:21.640
I help them with their cases

14:21.720 --> 14:24.080
and I wouldn’t necessarily write
a report on that.

14:24.160 --> 14:26.120
Were you able to compare

14:26.360 --> 14:29.320
the results of your analysis of...

14:30.040 --> 14:33.080
the reports that he wrote
with his testimony?

14:33.480 --> 14:35.120
Yes, I was.

14:36.280 --> 14:41.080
How many cases were there
in total in which Agent Deaver

14:41.160 --> 14:45.920
just observed bloodstains
either at the scene,

14:46.240 --> 14:49.520
at the SBI laboratory,
or by looking at photos?

14:50.240 --> 14:51.880
Only 54.

14:52.000 --> 14:54.720
In how many of those cases
did Agent Deaver provide

14:54.800 --> 14:57.560
a bloodstain pattern analysis opinion?

14:57.760 --> 14:58.600
Thirty-six.

14:58.680 --> 15:00.760
In how many of those cases

15:00.840 --> 15:05.440
did Agent Deaver actually go
to the scene of an event?

15:05.640 --> 15:10.960
Well, he went to 17 different scenes
between 1987 and 2003.

15:11.040 --> 15:12.960
How many cases were there

15:13.040 --> 15:15.760
in which Agent Deaver performed

15:15.840 --> 15:19.920
tests or experiments
before the Peterson case?

15:20.440 --> 15:21.320
Three.

15:22.280 --> 15:24.360
- Only three.
- What was the date

15:24.440 --> 15:28.880
of the last experiment that Agent Deaver
conducted on his own

15:29.520 --> 15:31.720
before the Peterson case?

15:32.360 --> 15:36.160
Back in 1991.
Eleven years before.

15:36.400 --> 15:40.640
How many cases where there in which
Agent Deaver, before the Peterson case,

15:40.720 --> 15:44.280
- found a precise point of impact?
- Zero.

15:44.360 --> 15:47.920
I think Agent Deaver also gave
some testimony about falls

15:48.000 --> 15:52.080
- and investigating falls, correct?
- That is correct. And stairs.

15:52.280 --> 15:54.160
Have you ever analyzed...

15:54.640 --> 15:59.960
bloodstain evidence from a situation
that was known to be a fall?

16:02.040 --> 16:03.120
Well...

16:03.960 --> 16:08.320
yes, I have been to
probably fifteen times where

16:08.680 --> 16:11.600
it was reported that a fall had occurred.

16:12.080 --> 16:14.960
Probably five or six of those times

16:15.240 --> 16:17.640
I was in agreement
that a fall was involved.

16:18.120 --> 16:21.520
The rest of the those, I was not
in agreement that a fall was involved

16:21.600 --> 16:25.040
or created the spatters,
the patterns that were seen there.

16:27.040 --> 16:30.720
Mr. Guerette,
how many of Agent Deaver's cases

16:30.800 --> 16:34.720
did you find in which
he had gone to the scene of a fall

16:34.800 --> 16:36.760
to analyze it in some way?

16:37.120 --> 16:40.760
Well, I checked every word
on every page in these documents

16:40.840 --> 16:43.280
and the word "falls" never occurred.

16:45.000 --> 16:48.200
- That’s all I have, Your Honor. Thank you.
- Alright, you can come down, sir.

