Hey!

17:11.720 --> 17:13.800
Good to see...
Oh, look at those teeth!

17:15.079 --> 17:17.560
So, are you alive, or what?
Are you alive?

17:17.680 --> 17:20.400
Are you alive?
You've been hobbling around all day.

17:20.480 --> 17:21.560
