17:41.160 --> 17:42.640
Either way, it's amazing.

17:42.720 --> 17:44.960
Well, here it is!

17:45.040 --> 17:49.720
So with any kind of luck,
I'll be out of here, you know...

17:50.840 --> 17:51.720
soon.

17:51.800 --> 17:54.160
Obviously, that's what
we're all hoping for.

