Yes, sir.

19:36.680 --> 19:38.480
- Time's up, sir.
- Okay.

19:38.560 --> 19:39.560
I gotta go.

19:40.360 --> 19:43.000
- OK.
- I love you very much, Dad.

19:43.160 --> 19:45.160
And put it there.

19:45.600 --> 19:47.920
OK. I love you and I'm so glad
to see you again.

