41:35.920 --> 41:38.760
that belongs to Michael King’s company,
Reliant Monitoring.

41:38.840 --> 41:40.080
We will make you a copy and make...

41:40.160 --> 41:41.200
What is today?

41:41.280 --> 41:43.840
- 12/15, that ought to be right.
- Today is 12/15.

41:46.360 --> 41:48.000
"This is your current address."

41:49.440 --> 41:51.760
I'll be able to finally become a Buddhist!

41:51.840 --> 41:53.000
It should be okay.

41:54.960 --> 41:56.080
Om!

41:56.160 --> 41:59.040
- Spoiled already.
- Oh, he’s a momma’s boy.

41:59.120 --> 42:00.480
Oh, right.

42:00.720 --> 42:01.960
We’ll change that.

42:02.040 --> 42:03.400
We’ll change that.

42:07.440 --> 42:10.400
Well, you guys both ended up
momma’s boys too, right?

42:10.480 --> 42:12.000
Only this guy right here.

42:15.920 --> 42:18.280
- Well, champagne.
- So, champagne.

42:23.960 --> 42:28.640
I cannot tell you how much I appreciate
what you all have done

42:30.320 --> 42:34.640
and how long you have fought
and stayed by my side, so...

42:35.720 --> 42:38.280
- To you! Thank you.
